The paper discusses the reconstruction of 3D scenes from multiple views, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also focuses on the surfacing of these scenes, which falls under computer graphics (cs.GR). The applications mentioned in the paper, such as robotics (cs.RO), industrial design, and hard surface modeling, suggest that the paper may also be relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
